txt.en: Increases your hatchling's health and reduces its skill cooldowns. You gain increased Physical Mitigation.\n\nOnly one Hatchling trait can be equipped at a time.
Increases your hatchling's health and reduces its skill cooldowns. You gain increased Physical Mitigation.\n\nOnly one Hatchling trait can be equipped at a time.

Your hatchling gains the following:
   +25% Health
   +10% Power
   +20% Mitigations
  +5% Attack Speed
   +15% Outgoing Damage
   +5% Critical Chance
  +5% Evade Chance 
  Enhanced Skills

Your hatchling gains the following:
   +125% Health
   -10% Power
   +20% Mitigations
  +5% Attack Speed
   +25% Melee Damage
   +25% Critical Chance
  +15% Evade Chance 
  Enhanced Skills
